

     The Magnolia CMS project has announced the initial release of Magnolia for Documents 1.0. "...an easy-to-use, standards-based document-management-system (DMS) based on JSR-170. Magnolia for Documents enables you to easily manage documents through a web-based application, assign customizable meta-data and fine-grained access-rights to each document and store, publish, categorize and retrieve documents efficiently."
   

